  ('medical-tech-moex-21422', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-092-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '失血後，血壓下降會引發下列何種現象？ 頸動脈竇 (carotid sinus) 通往延腦之舌咽神經活動性增加 頸動脈竇通往延腦之舌咽神經活動性減少 頸動脈竇通往延腦之交感神經活動性增加 延腦通往腎血管之副交感神經活動性增加', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:18+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "caad7201cfd2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f5d53904488e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "092170", "c": "105", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "092", "exam_name": "092年第二次醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、獸醫人員、心理師、呼吸治療師考試", "original_question_number": 15, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-21423', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-092-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關正常人的肋膜腔 (intrapleural space) 內之液體的敘述，下列何者正確？ 此液體可供肺組織與肋膜間作氣體交換  此液體可調節肺組織淋巴液的總量 此液體可減少肺組織與肋膜間的摩擦  此液體控制肺組織血流量', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:18+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "caad7201cfd2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f5d53904488e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "092170", "c": "105", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "092", "exam_name": "092年第二次醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、獸醫人員、心理師、呼吸治療師考試", "original_question_number": 16, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-21424', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-092-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者是專指呼吸道的傳導區 (conducting zone)？ 鼻腔到口腔兩個區域 鼻腔到氣管 (trachea) 的區域 氣管到末端小支氣管 (terminal bronchioles) 的區域 呼吸性小支氣管 (respiratory bronchioles) 到肺泡的區域', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:18+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "caad7201cfd2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f5d53904488e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "092170", "c": "105", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "092", "exam_name": "092年第二次醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、獸醫人員、心理師、呼吸治療師考試", "original_question_number": 17, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
